.DT
ignore
$MUDNAME$ player help
ignore

.SH Name
.SI 5
ignore - ignore someone
.EI

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
ignore
ignore <name>
unignore <name>
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
Ignore allows you to block all tells from a player.  Unignore will remove a player from your ignore list and ignore on its own will tell you who you are currently ignoring. 'unignore all' will stop you ignoring anyone.

Ignore will also block out all shouts, talker chats and so on.  It blocks
everything you think of doing with the other person.
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
> ignore shiannar
You are now ignoring Shiannar.

> unignore shiannar
Shiannar has been removed from your list of ignored players.

> ignore
You are not ignoring anyone.
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
earmuffs
.EI
